text: Kholodny Klyuch () is a rural locality (a village) in Shabagishsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 317 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 17 km from Yermolayevo, 12 km from Shabagish. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Kholodny Klyuch
